  "lastUpdatedOn": "2012-10-12",
  "religion": "Darren Criss went to Catholic schools growing up, but now he has a general kind of spirituality that involves belief in a higher power of some sort.",
  "politicalViews": "He's a Democrat and very involved in gay rights.",
  "author": "Caitlin Frye",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 1
    },
    {
      "parentId": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Darren Criss was born and raised mostly in San Francisco, California with a four-year stint in Honolulu, Hawaii."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 2
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Criss appears to have been raised Catholic since he went to several Catholic schools growing up.",
      "sourceTitle": "Darren Criss, former Stuart Hall for Boys student, finds role on 'Glee.'",
      "sourceUrl": "http://z5.sacredsf.org/~broadview/?p=3037"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " But his faith takes a slightly more ambiguous form these days. Referring to the famous atheist, Richard Dawkins, Criss said:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 4,
      "parentId": 3
    },
    {
      "parentId": 4,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I believe in things greater than us, and I believe in love and human beings, and I believe in reverence and spirituality and divinity. Whether or not that is embodied in whatever Dawkins might call God isn't really important to me. I just believe in the greater something and I believe in good people.",
      "sourceTitle": "Jared Sagal interviews Darren Criss of GLEE ( Part One ).",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f1rYlKU1bTQ"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 5
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "And even if he doesn't consider himself Catholic anymore, he appears to hold Jesus in pretty high regard. When asked who would be on his ideal "
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "link",
      "text": "Comic-Con",
      "sourceUrl": "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/San_Diego_Comic-Con_International"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " panel, Criss named \"Jesus Christ of Nazareth\" among others including Christopher Walken, "
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "link",
      "text": "Gandhi",
      "sourceUrl": "http://hollowverse.com/mohandas-karamchand-gandhi/"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": ", and John Lennon.",
      "sourceTitle": "Darren Criss Dishes on Comic-Con, Harry Potter and, of Course, 'Glee.'",
      "sourceUrl": "http://popcrush.com/darren-criss-comic-con-harry-potter-glee/"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " I'd stay for that show.\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": 6
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "The Politics of "
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "emphasis",
      "text": "Glee"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 7
    },
    {
      "parentId": 7,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Darren Criss is definitely a Democrat. He performed at an Obama fundraiser focused on the LGBT community in 2012, and he seemed pretty excited to give the President a fist bump at the event.",
      "sourceTitle": "Video: Darren talks politics in Glee and meeting President Obama on Strombo Tonight.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://darrencrissweb.com/video-darren-talks-politics-in-glee-and-meeting-president-obama-on-george-stroumboulopoulos-tonight/"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 8
    },
    {
      "parentId": 8,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "And that fundraiser was only one of many things he's done to show his support for a cause that's deeply important to him:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 9
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 10,
      "parentId": 9
    },
    {
      "parentId": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I grew up in San Francisco and I did theater growing up and so I was kind of inadvertently raised by the gay community, and it's something that's always been very prominent in my social consciousness as far as what really mattered to me.",
      "sourceTitle": "Darren Criss Shows His Support For The Trevor Project & Talks 'Glee.'",
      "sourceUrl": "http://watch.accesshollywood.com/video/darren-criss-shows-his-support-for-the-trevor-project-talks-glee/1314858455001"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 11
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Criss automatically entered the political landscape when he took the role of an openly gay teen on the popular TV show "
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "emphasis",
      "text": "Glee"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": ". The show has been criticized by some conservatives, namely radio host Glenn Beck who called its message \"horrifying.\"",
      "sourceTitle": "Glenn Beck Discovers Glee Three Years After Its Premiere, Plans Conservative Rival Series.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.vanityfair.com/online/oscars/2012/06/glenn-beck-glee-rival-series-casting"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " Criss has gladly embraced the political side of his role:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 13,
      "parentId": 12
    },
    {
      "parentId": 13,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "It's been really special for me because the character is something that I'm very personal about, something I believe in, and it just so happens to be attached to a socio-political package that I'm very invested in.",
      "sourceTitle": "Darren Criss on Ellen (02-02-11).",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c_HdpkTaN1g"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 14
    },
    {
      "parentId": 14,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Among several other charities, the actor supports the Trevor Project which aims to prevent suicides among LGBT teens. Seems right up his alley."
    }
  ],
